						<li>All art prints carry <strong>25% flat discount</strong> on the listed prices</li>
						<li>There is no minimum or maximum order value</li>
						<li>Just add the products you like to the cart and apply the coupon <strong>"MAR25"</strong> in your shopping cart</li>
						<li>If you have logged in and it's your first order the coupon "FIRST15" is applied by default. 
							You can apply "MAR25" to avail the offer.</li>
						<li>This offer starts on 19th Mar 2022 and ends on 27th Mar 2022
						<li>This offer cannot be combined with other discount offers</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row mt-4">			
			<div class = "col-12 d-flex justify-content-center d-flex-row">
