			</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row">			
			<div class = "col-12 col-md-6  sign-up-right">
				<img src="{% static 'img/main-image/paintings_online_15_off.jpg' %}" alt="" class="img-fluid" width="500">
			</div>
			<div class = "col-12 col-md-6 " style = "margin:auto;">
				<div class = "row text-center" style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color:#11b6bd;">
					<div class = "col-12 text-center">"FIRST15"</div>
				</div>
				<div style="margin-top:20px; color:#665d6f;">
					<ul>
						<li>All art prints carry 15% off</li>
						<li>There is no minimum or maximum order value</li>
						<li>Just add the products you like to the cart and apply the coupon "FIRST15"</li>
						<li>If you have logged in and it's your first order the coupon "FIRST15" is applied automatically</li>
						<li>This offer cannot be combined with other discount offers</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row mt-4">			
			<div class = "col-12 d-flex justify-content-center d-flex-row">
				<span class = "offer_num">3</span>
				<span class = "offer_text" >FREE DELIVERY</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class = "row">			
			<div class = "col-12 col-md-6  sign-up-right">
				<img src="{% static 'img/free_shipping.jpg' %}" alt="" class="img-fluid" width="500">
			</div>
			<div class = "col-12 col-md-6 " style = "margin:auto;">
				<div style="margin-top:20px; color:#665d6f;">
					<ul>
						<li>All orders are shipped free of cost</li>
						<li>No minimum or maximum order value</li>
						<li>We ship anywhere in India</li>
						<li>Shipments to other countries are charged at actuals</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
